author: China Insights-SOHTV
description:
#replacement #meal #ai 
What if your meals came in cans and your break time shrank to minutes?
A new “nutrition trend” is sweeping across busy cities—meals without flavor, color, or joy. Just powder and water, and you're back to work.
From fast fixes to ultra-processed kits, efficiency now trumps well-being.
And guess what? It's marketed as freedom.
We explore how modern routines have reshaped what we eat, how we live, and how easy it is to lose track of what being “alive” should feel like.
title: Snowpiercer Has Already Started｜China Insights｜
